trans-unit.source: Defines a service that can be obtained from an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"></xref> for the purpose of starting a new workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: 가져올 수 있는 서비스를 정의 하는 <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext"> </xref> 새 워크플로 인스턴스를 시작할 수 있도록 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Starts the workflow of designated <xref:System.Type> providing the running instance with a <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase.Dictionary*> that contains runtime parameters.
trans-unit.target: 시작의 워크플로에 지정 된 <xref:System.Type>사용 하 여 실행 중인 인스턴스를 제공 하는 <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase.Dictionary*>런타임 매개 변수가 포함 된.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase.Dictionary*> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase.Dictionary*> that contains runtime parameters for the workflow.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase.Dictionary*>워크플로에 대 한 런타임 매개 변수를 포함 하는.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryBase.Dictionary*>

trans-unit.source: The instance ID of the workflow that is started.
